channel.title: I have something to tell you all
channel.description:
Hello, You all know me as D E C O Y.
I have something to tell you all. I never had a server, I never had anything advanced.
I am doing this to try to get a second chance at Mscp.
I will not lie again. and Moparisthebest, im sorry for spreading rumors.
Im just tired of seeing the same old "An error has occured!" page.
sorry.
- D E C O Y
